short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome Extension for Chatbot Arena Conversations

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is the Chrome extension for Taiwan LLM Chatbot Arena, users can have conversations with different LLMs on the platform and rate the performance of LLMs. You can install it as a Chrome extension so that you may talk with the LLMs while viewing other pages.

This project is meant for a crowdsourced benchmark of LLM's performance among users in Taiwan.

By using this website, you agree with our privacy agreement.
https://chatbot-arena-woad.vercel.app/privacy.txt
